The quick-create dialog can't work properly in admin areas because of how custom fields are defined: the javascript required to make custom fields work is only targeted at the {{atl.general}} context.

We'd like to make the Quick Create dialog work in admin. However, doing this would require plugins for Custom Fields to change their contexts -- this work requires significant changes to how Custom Fields define and deliver their assets: see JRA-36936 for the details of this work.

